{
  "stem": "11723.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, at that point, since they didn't see the star, they even gave us seats because they were with children.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And a few minutes later, maybe an hour later-- I don't know, because as a child you don't remember time so well-- somebody noticed the star.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And immediately they, they threw us off the seats.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They threw us off the seats.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were screaming and yelling at us, dirty Jew and stinking Jew and who needs you?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you should drop dead and your kids should drop dead.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, terrible, terrible curses and everything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the Hungarian soldiers were on the train, too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they came.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And instead of helping us out, they were, in unison with the rest of the train, they were going to throw us off the train, the moving train.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And at that point some Serb soldiers showed up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I Don't know how old these people were on the train, but they were.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the Serbs were saying to the Hungarians, what kind of people are you?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You want to throw innocent little kids off the train?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You're supposed to keep order here, not to help the crowds riot here.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so then the Hungarians were, of course, greater in number than the Serbs, and they were telling them, what are you, Jew lovers?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What do you care what we do with these stinking Jews?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so a fight broke out, and my father said to my mother, let's get as fast out of here as we can, because you know what happens.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "At the end, it's always the Jew who's gonna get it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we made our way through the train from car to car until the last car.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my father said to my mother, you know what?",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
